thread.title: BRIEF-Guangdong Jiaying Pharmaceutical to swing to loss in FY 2017

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Guangdong Jiaying Pharmaceutical to swing to loss in FY 2017

organizations.name: reuters) - guangdong jiaying pharmaceutical co ltd

text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Guangdong Jiaying Pharmaceutical Co Ltd
* Says it expected FY 2017 net loss to be 59 million yuan to 69 million yuan versus net profit of 55.2 million yuan year ago
* Comments that net loss of unit as main reason for the forecast
